cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction of environments using depth sensors and CAD models. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of depth sensors for environment mapping, which is relevant to robotics applications. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper introduces a novel approach for aligning CAD models to 3D scans using deep reinforcement learning. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with 3D modeling and rendering of environments. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper introduces a learning-based approach for aligning CAD models to 3D scans.
